FAQ

Common questions, answered.

Everything you need to know before starting scope, timelines, and how we work across build launch scale.

Can I start at any phase?

Yes. Engagement is modular start with Validate, jump into Build, or begin at Launch/Scale if you're already shipping. View Packages & Services

What do you build, exactly?

We build digital products end-to-end: AI MVPs, mobile apps, and the launch + growth systems around them (landing pages, tracking, paid ads, and content/marketing). Explore Solutions

Who do you work with?

Tech founders building AI/apps, healthcare clinics improving patient acquisition, and Shopify brands focused on conversion and retention. Choose Your Track

How do you keep delivery predictable?

Weekly demos, one shared backlog, and stage gates for decisions and sign-offs so priorities stay clear and scope doesn't drift. See How We Work

Do you build AI agents and LLM features?

Yes agents, RAG, and workflow automation. We prioritize production readiness: evaluation, guardrails, and monitoring so it performs beyond a demo. AI SaaS MVP Launch

Do you support HIPAA-aware delivery for clinics?

Yes. We use privacy-first workflows and healthcare-appropriate handling for systems that touch patient data. Clinic Growth System

How do you measure success?

We define success metrics upfront (e.g., booked appointments, pilot activation, conversion rate, retention) and instrument tracking so progress is visible week to week. View Playbook

How fast can we launch?

Typical ranges: Validate (24 weeks), Build (612 weeks), Launch (24 weeks). Scale is ongoing with monthly experimentation and content/marketing execution. View Playbook See Packages

What if I only need help with one area?

That works. You can engage us for a focused sprint (UX fixes, analytics setup, landing page, paid ads setup, retention audit, SEO/content plan) or expand into a full build scale engagement. Explore Packages

Can I see examples of your work?

Yes browse case studies mapped to each track: Menovia (AI MVP), Vascular (Clinic Growth), Al-Mahfza (Relaunch), Hartalega (Corporate), Larovie (Shopify Growth). View Case Studies
